title: Fabric DJ Mix Series COMPLETE 1-71 [House, Techno] [MP3 V0 and 3
description:
The Fabric night club in London hosts alternating shows each month, Fabric and FabricLive, which feature famous DJs from around the world. These special mixes are recorded and released on CD. The Fabric series is better known for house and techno.
